channel.title: Can't get onto ANY server
channel.description: I tried dozens of servers on client 3.2. Every each sponsored, and every from the first page. I got many msgs like: error connecting to server, no response from loginserver please try using a different world, error connecting to server; must be down, unexpected server response please try using a different world, unable to connect; bad session id. I have no idea what's going on.. i just want to play any server, mess around for a moment and leave :/! Can you help me, or send me any working server IP?

item.title: Can't get onto ANY server
item.dc:creator: @Tutorial Tutorial
item.description:
@Tutorial wrote:

Seems like you have a strict firewall. Have you ever been able to play any type of server? If not, that means your computer is not allowing you to connect to port 43594 (which is the default port for servers).
